    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this indie game created by a single developer, you'll discover a story shrouded in mystery across a variety of pixel-art-style areas, with a variety of music for each setting. All of this is accompanied by strategic battles between Papling, 2D platforming challenges, and various minigames (there always has to be a fishing minigame in an RPG).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the pages of a mysterious book called <strong>Paplion</strong>, strange monsters can be found. Those are called <strong>Papling</strong>, monsters born from paper. After being absorbed by the book, you will meet your partner <strong>Papling</strong> and together you will go in an adventure through the chapters of <strong>Paplion</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/04f83e1274e713e896281d975e08704c.poster.avif?t=1763842248\" width=64 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/04f83e1274e713e896281d975e08704c.webm?t=1763842248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Papling</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find more than 100 different <strong>Papling</strong> to <strong>befriend</strong> and add them to your <strong>deck</strong>. Of the 12 starter Papling, your partner will be a reflection of your personality! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/2948702acb7787066c92ab8acbd95098.apng?t=1763842248\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/2948702acb7787066c92ab8acbd95098.poster.avif?t=1763842248\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=192 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose their evolution line</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Papling</strong> have <strong>3 evolutive stages</strong>. Those that aren't in the last stage can choose between 3 different evolutions to evolve, becoming stronger and gaining <strong>new abilities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/dfe8191390533eae6e688ec0d4e059e2.avif?t=1763842248\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple paths and replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paplion</strong> has <strong>6 chapters,</strong> each of them with its own world to explore and you can choose in which order you will play them. Also, each of them has each own story, divided in two different paths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/35c15d341c6b6c8126fa41a766bd2da3.apng?t=1763842248\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/35c15d341c6b6c8126fa41a766bd2da3.poster.avif?t=1763842248\" class=\"bb_img\" width=576 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soundtrack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paplion has an extensive, varied and high quality soundtrack with more than 100 tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/d16caac19488d763d7c4880f2248b9a3.webp?t=1763842248\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/d16caac19488d763d7c4880f2248b9a3.webp?t=1763842248\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/d16caac19488d763d7c4880f2248b9a3.webp?t=1763842248\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize the main character with different hats, suits and shoes you will find through your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/938d73e3c76616bebbdffb6346f5cab0.apng?t=1763842248\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037480/extras/938d73e3c76616bebbdffb6346f5cab0.poster.avif?t=1763842248\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >??????</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Nztufsjft boe tfdsfut gps uif dvsjpvt poft</span></p>",
